[
    {
        "content": "<p>I have two different minimum reproductions that seem to demonstrate the failure in two slightly different ways:</p>\n<p>Notice that in the first example, <code>dbg list.len()</code> correctly prints <code>1</code>, but that <code>dbg $idx</code> prints <code>{}</code>. However, in the second example with the <code>while</code> loop, <code>dbg list.len()</code> prints a floating point number, and <code>dbg $idx</code> prints a <em>different</em> floating point number, from which the loop begins iterating.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Ruby\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"no\">Min</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[].</span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">find_last_indxex</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">List</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">U64</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">find_last_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">dbg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">var</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">dbg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"n\">expect</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">]-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">find_last_index</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>$ roc test Min.roc --no-cache\n[dbg] 1\n[dbg] {}\nAll (1) tests passed in 31.5 ms.\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Ruby\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"no\">Min</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[].</span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">find_last_indxex</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">List</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">U64</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">find_last_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">dbg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">var</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">list</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">dbg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">while</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">dbg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$idx</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"n\">expect</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">]-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">find_last_index</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">NotFound</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>$ roc test Min.roc --no-cache\n[dbg] -113427455640312821166.756031859729104895\n[dbg] 756.316507022091616257\n[dbg] 755.316507022091616257\n[dbg] 754.316507022091616257\n...\n[dbg] 0.316507022091616257\n[dbg] -0.683492977908383743\nAll (1) tests passed in 39.4 ms.\n</code></pre></div>",
